OL,6,FThe government is reportedly looking
OL,7,Fat the eligibility criteria for the
OL,8,Fpersonal independence payment (PIP),
OL,9,Fwhich is money for people with extra
OL,10,Fcare needs or mobility needs as a
OL,11,Fresult of a disability.
OL,13,FThis has sparked an outcry from some
OL,14,FLabour MPs, with one telling the PA
OL,15,Fnews there has been a lack of
OL,16,Fcommunication from ministers.
