OL,6,FMinisters insist that reform is
OL,7,Fnecessary given that the number of
OL,8,Fpeople in England and Wales claiming
OL,9,Feither sickness or disability benefit
OL,10,Fhas soared from 2.8 million to about
OL,11,F4.0 million since 2019.
OL,13,FThe benefits bill has risen with this
OL,14,Fincrease, reaching #48 billion in 2023-
OL,15,F24, and is forecast to continue rising
OL,16,Fto #67 billion in 2029-30 ` a level
OL,17,Fthat would exceed the current schools
OL,18,Fbudget and the government regards as
OL,19,Funsustainable.
