OL,6,FHe told the BBC's Sunday With Laura
OL,7,FKuenssberg: "I haven't seen the
OL,8,Fproposals but you've seen the
OL,9,Fbriefing, you've seen the speculation,
OL,10,FI think the moral of the story is wait
